  "title": "Accounts executive",
  "description": "<p>1.      Manage and oversee the day-to-day financial operations, including accounts receivable,accounts payable, and general ledger reconciliation</p><p>2.      Prepare and analyse financial statements, such as balance sheets, income statements,and cash flow reports</p><p>3.      Ensure compliance with relevant accounting standards, laws, and regulations<br /></p><p>4.      Strong understanding of financial accounting principles, practices, and reporting requirements</p><p>5.      Proficient in the use of accounting software (MYOB)</p><p>6.      Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>7.      Ability to work independently and manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment</p>",
